with BankAccountDAO testing, we have to ensure the following functions will be executed correctly:
Get method:
    1:Get Account by a given account Number
    2:Get account by a give id
    3. The medthod get will output null value if no accout exists
    4.Get the whole list from the database
Update method:
    5. update an account existing in the database
    6. update an account which doest not exist in the database
    7. create (and update) an account which is not already in the database
Delete method:
    8. Delete an account by ID, account number
    9. Delete the whole rows in a table

with TransactionDAO testing:
    10. save a transaction
    11. get the list of an account's transactions which is executed
    12. get the list of an account's transactions which is executed in an interval of time
    13. get the list of n closest transactions








